4: Increase Attack Speed by 60% (L49)<br>
<br>
Burnout IV<br>
2: Increase Armor Class (AC) by 17 (L55)<br>
3: Increase Strength by 60 (L55)<br>
4: Increase Attack Speed by 65% (L55)<br>
<br>
Only thing you gain is 3 ac and 10 str if your already capped at 60%<br>
